function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	Hydra.QActorSetConversationStatus(idSurvivorChapel, false)
	
	idSurvivorFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("QST_Hawe_ByThree_SurvivorFollower")
	Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idSurvivorFollower)
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convEnterChapel, idSelf, idSurvivorFollower)
	Hydra.ActorDisableAI(idSurvivorFollower)
	Hydra.QActorSheath(idSurvivorFollower)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idSurvivorFollower, idSurvivorChapel, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idSurvivorFollower, idSurvivorChapel)
	Hydra.QActorDelete(idSurvivorFollower)
	Hydra.QActorEventSend(idSurvivorFollower, "StaticSev")
	
	--Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idSurvivorFollower)
	

end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

	Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(convGoodbye, idSelf, idSurvivorChapel)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idSurvivorChapel, convGoodbye)
	Hydra.QActorSetConversationStatus(idSurvivorChapel, true)

end
